dct_title_s: Pacific Coast, Pt. Buchon to Pt. Pinos, California
dct_description_sm: "Topography executed between 1854 and 1891. Hydrography [executed between] 1851 and 1891."
Relief shown by hachures, shading and spot heights; depth shown by soundings.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Includes notes and charts on lighthouses, buoys, tides, etc.
